title: Total Rehab! In Unit Laundry! Stainless Steel! Pets Welcome!
posting_body: ['Call Apartment Guys at 773-549-3474 and ask for reference #2202259.', ' Live right in the heart of Lincoln Park surrounded by some of the best restaurants and nightlife in the city!', 'This recently renovated one bedroom  features a freshly updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances including your own private laundry in your apartment as well as a dishwasher.', 'It also features a  renovated bathroom with new fixtures and countertops, and a spacious bedroom and living area!', 'Door-person, fitness center, and laundry on site!', 'Lake Michigan is only a couple of blocks away from your door.', 'Easy commute to Downtown/Loop!', 'Parking available for a fee.', 'Prices are subject to change.', '***Photos may be of a similar unit.****For faster response best to call or text 773-549-3474 with reference #2202259']
